This is a small but useful module for Kohana 3.

Just extend Controller_Xhtml and use the singletons Xhtml and Head where required.
See the code for details.
I'll provide examples and other documentation soon.

Version 0.1 (2010-01-25)
 - Basic operation
 - Xhtml singleton class
 - Head singleton class
 - Abstract Controller_Xhtml extending Controller_Template
 - Mapping controller $template to body
 
 Version 0.2 (2010-01-28)
 - Adjusted defaults handling, now global configs are overwritten by controller properties
 - Added an ajax property to the controller
 - Added check for template property to before()



